----- stdout -----
Manage accounts (list, create, archive)

Usage: borrow-checker account [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list     List all active accounts
  create   Create a new account
  archive  Archive an account (hides it from active lists; data is preserved)
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json               Emit machine-readable JSON instead of human-readable output [env: BC_JSON=]
      --db-path <DB_PATH>  Path to the SQLite database file [env: BC_DB_PATH=[TEMP_DIR]/test.db]
  -h, --help               Print help
